These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-1::.
There 6 different types of food: cauliflower, grapefruit, zucchini, raspberry, pumpkin, banana
City: london, liverpool, boston, rome, san-francisco, colone
 1. the person eating zucchini is in an odd position##4
 2. the person eating banana is somewhere to the left of the person eating grapefruit##5
 3. the person eating pumpkin is not the person traveling to san-francisco##6
 4. the person eating raspberry is somewhere to the left of the person eating grapefruit##5
 5. the person traveling to san-francisco is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to boston##5
 6. the person traveling to liverpool is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to boston##5
 7. the person traveling to san-francisco is not the person eating grapefruit##6
 8. the person traveling to colone is in an odd position##4
 9. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere between the person traveling to colone and the person eating raspberry##7
10. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
11. the person traveling to colone is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to london##5
12. the person traveling to colone is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to rome##5
13. the person traveling to london is the person eating cauliflower##1
14. the person traveling to boston is somewhere to the left of the person eating pumpkin##5
15. the person eating banana is the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Food   | raspberry   | cauliflower | zucchini   | banana     | grapefruit    | pumpkin   |
| City           | san-francisco | london   | colone | rome | boston | liverpool |

