.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-2::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, soy-milk, sprite, iced-tea, tea, milk
There are 6 different favourite colors: red, emerald, mauve, lilac, white, fuchsia
 1. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5
 2. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 3. the person who likes white is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person who likes lilac##3
 5. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who likes white##1
 6. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 7. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person drinking tea is not the person who likes white##6
10. the person who likes red is somewhere between the person who likes fuchsia and the person who likes lilac##7
11. the person who likes mauve is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
12. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
13. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left or right of the person who likes red##3
14. the person who likes fuchsia is in an even position##4
15. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the left of the person who likes lilac##5
16. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who likes red##1
17. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere between the person who likes emerald and the person drinking tea##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |     5      |    6     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | milk | iced-tea | tea     | sprite      | almond-milk |
| Color           | emerald         | mauve        | white   | lilac | red | fuchsia    |

