 9. the electrician is on the left or right of the person who likes red##3
10. the journalist is somewhere between the person who likes aquamarine and the person who likes red##7
11. the paramedic is in an odd position##4
12. the electrician is on the left or right of the person who likes ebony##3
13. the person who likes ebony is somewhere to the left of the electrician##5
14. the person who likes pink is somewhere to the left of the paramedic##5

