.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-4::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: september, march, february, january, december, october
6 different games are played: mah-jongg, poker, monopoly, canasta, backgammon, bridge
 1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 2. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
 3. the person playing poker is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##5
 4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 5. the person playing poker is not the person who's birthday is in december##6
 6. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who's birthday is in december##7
 7. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's birthday is in october##7
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who's birthday is in january##7
10. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
11. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
12. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the left of the person playing poker##5
13. the person playing monopoly is the person who's birthday is in january##1
14. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |   3   |       4       |    5    |   6   |
| Birthday      | january | march | october | february | december | september   |
| Game   | monopoly  | canasta      | mah-jongg | backgammon     | bridge | poker |

