 5. the person watching comedy movies is between the russian and the person watching documentary movies##2
 6. the malaysian is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching sports movies##5
 8. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere between the person watching epic movies and the person watching family movies##7
 9. the malaysian is on the left or right of the polish##3
10. the british is on the far right##1
11. the russian is the person watching disaster movies##1
12. the argentine is not the person watching disaster movies##6
13. the polish is on the left of the italian##1
