 5. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
 6. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the person who likes light-blue##5
 7. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5
 8. the person who likes black is not the owner of the hedgehog##6
