10. the person who likes green is somewhere to the left of the person who likes black##5
11. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
12. the person who likes green is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
13. the person who likes turquise is on the far right##1
14. the owner of the turtle is somewhere between the owner of the hedgehog and the owner of the bird##7
15. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the bird##5

.:: Answer ::.
