.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-19::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: disaster, western, action, superhero, musical, epic
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, game, bongani, ritmeester, bolivar, tiparillo
 1. the bongani-smoker is the person watching action movies##1
 2. the person watching disaster movies is in an odd position##4
 3. the person watching western movies is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
 4. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
 5. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the left of the bongani-smoker##5
 6. the person watching disaster movies is between the person watching musical movies and the chaman-smoker##2
 7. the tiparillo-smoker is somewhere to the left of the game-smoker##5
 8. the bolivar-smoker is on the left or right of the chaman-smoker##3
 9. the person watching western movies is in an odd position##4
10. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the right of the tiparillo-smoker##5
11. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
12. the bolivar-smoker is somewhere between the person watching action movies and the game-smoker##7
13. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching epic movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |   2    |     3     |   4    |  5   |     6      |
| Movie-Genre         | western   | musical | disaster      | superhero | epic  | action   |
| Cigar   | ritmeester | tiparillo  | game | chaman   | bolivar | bongani |

