.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-20::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: scooter, taxi, jet-ski, motorbike, snowmobile, bus
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: tulip, amaryllis, marigold, poppy, balloon-flower, lily
 1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
 2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the right of the person who growsmarigold##5
 4. the person driving the scooter is somewhere between the person who growspoppy and the person who growsamaryllis##7
 5. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the right of the person who growspoppy##5
 8. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
 9. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere to the left of the person who growsmarigold##5
10. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere to the right of the person who growslily##5
11. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
12. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the right of the person who growspoppy##5
13. the person driving the taxi is somewhere between the person driving the scooter and the person driving the jet-ski##7
14. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
15. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2      |     3      |     4     |      5      |     6      |
| Transport   | jet-ski         | motorbike | taxi | scooter   | bus | snowmobile  |
| Flower     | balloon-flower | poppy  | marigold  | lily | amaryllis  | tulip |

 